9:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose prose-lg prose-headings:font-serif prose-headings:text-foreground prose-headings:tracking-tight prose-a:text-teal prose-a:decoration-teal/30 hover:prose-a:decoration-teal prose-img:rounded-2xl max-w-none","children":[["$","h1","h1-0",{"children":"Phi-3 vs Llama 3 for Local AI"}],"\n",["$","p","p-0",{"children":["When selecting a model for local deployments, parameter count dictates your hardware requirements. Currently, two models dominate the sub-10B space: Meta's ",["$","strong","strong-0",{"children":"Llama 3 (8B)"}]," and Microsoft's ",["$","strong","strong-1",{"children":"Phi-3 (Mini 3.8B)"}],"."]}],"\n",["$","h2","h2-0",{"children":"Architectural Differences"}],"\n",["$","h3","h3-0",{"children":"Llama 3 (8B)"}],"\n",["$","ul","ul-0",{"children":["\n",["$","li","li-0",{"children":[["$","strong","strong-0",{"children":"Strengths"}],": Incredible nuance, vast generalized knowledge, highly capable of complex logical reasoning."]}],"\n",["$","li","li-1",{"children":[["$","strong","strong-0",{"children":"Hardware needed"}],": Minimum 8GB VRAM (with Q4 quantization) for comfortable speeds."]}],"\n"]}],"\n",["$","h3","h3-1",{"children":"Phi-3 Mini (3.8B)"}],"\n",["$","ul","ul-1",{"children":["\n",["$","li","li-0",{"children":[["$","strong","strong-0",{"children":"Strengths"}],": Trained heavily on \"textbook\" data. Unbelievably smart for its size, handles coding tasks exceptionally well."]}],"\n",["$","li","li-1",{"children":[["$","strong","strong-0",{"children":"Hardware needed"}],": Runs flawlessly on almost any modern laptop, even without a dedicated GPU."]}],"\n"]}],"\n",["$","h2","h2-1",{"children":"The Benchmark: Code Generation"}],"\n",["$","p","p-1",{"children":["We tested both models on a 0-shot prompt to generate a React ",["$","code","code-0",{"className":"bg-muted px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded-md font-mono text-sm text-teal before:content-none after:content-none","children":"useIntersectionObserver"}]," hook."]}],"\n",["$","p","p-2",{"children":[["$","strong","strong-0",{"children":"Llama 3"}]," provided a complete, robust solution with comments explaining the teardown phase.\n",["$","strong","strong-1",{"children":"Phi-3"}]," provided a highly optimized, concise solution but missed a specific edgecase regarding React's ",["$","code","code-0",{"className":"bg-muted px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded-md font-mono text-sm text-teal before:content-none after:content-none","children":"deps"}]," array."]}],"\n",["$","h2","h2-2",{"children":"Conclusion"}],"\n",["$","p","p-3",{"children":"If you have the RAM, Llama 3 provides a more robust conversational experience. If you are building background agents or running hardware-constrained devices, Phi-3 is unmatched."}]]}]
